         <div type="writingSession" n="1">
            <p>
               <note type="introduction">In <rs type="place" ref="pmb677">Breslau</rs>
               </note>
               <date when="19001201" n="1">1/12</date> Probe. Ankunft <rs type="person" ref="pmb14953">M. G.</rs>– <rs type="person" ref="pmb11910">Kerr</rs>; später <rs type="person" ref="pmb10815">Bahr</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pmb2167">Salten</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pmb2161">Bukovics</rs>.– Abd. Prem. <rs type="work" ref="pmb29857">Bea.</rs>– Viel Beifall, viel Opposition.– Schlechte Aufführung.–</p>
            <p>Bei <rs type="place" ref="pmb125">Hansen</rs>: – <rs type="person" ref="pmb2941">Loewe</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pmb27870">Schlesinger</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pmb2944">Runge</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pmb25498">Sternau</rs>, und die Gaeste.– <rs type="person" ref="pmb14953">M. G.</rs> weinte im Wagen mit mir und <rs type="person" ref="pmb11910">Kerr</rs> über die schlechte Aufführung.–</p>
         </div>
      </body>
